The '''Joint Interface Control Officer (JICO)''' is the senior multi-tactical data link interface control officer in support of joint [[task force]] operations. The JICO is responsible for effecting planning and management of the joint [[tactical data link]] network within a [[Theater (warfare)|theater of operations]].<ref>CJCSM 3115.01A</ref>
